item.title: Public Consultation 3
item.description: What should Menston’s new Scout and Guide hut look like? 🤷🏼‍♀️ Come along to have a look round Burley Scout and Guide HQ to see what we could achieve for our village! 👀 Saturday 6th January 10-12 noon This is a an opportunity to ask questions, share suggestions and brainstorm ideas for our future hut! 💬💡
